{{Otheruses|Silver|more=Bantha}}
The '''Silver Bantha''' was an award given to [[Droid/Legends|droid]] models for "excellence in industrial design". The [[GH-7 medical analysis unit|GH-7 medical droid]] won this award four times, according to a [[Chiewab Amalgamated Pharmaceuticals Company]] sales manual. It was named after the [[Bantha/Legends|banthas]] of [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]].

